*Pričati* smo o tome već nekoliko sati. (We've been talking about it for several hours.)

*Pričala* je o svojim problemima. (She was talking about her problems.)

*Pričalice* su se kroz cijeli dan. (They were talking all day long.)

*Pričam* ti odmah. (I'm telling you right away.)

*Pričaju* svi o tome. (Everybody is talking about it.)

*Pričahu* se o tome i prije. (They were talking about it before.)